CyberIllustrious V7.0: Refined and Stable

For version 7.0, I took a step back and really listened to the feedback from the community.
This update reintroduces elements of the older training, applied in a more balanced way, while carefully removing parts that didnt fit. On top of that, Ive selectively added new training with a very deliberate, controlled approach.

The result is a stable, reliable model that feels smoother to work with, produces cleaner and more consistent outputs, and responds better to the classic Illustrious style of prompting.

CyberIllustrious V7.0 aims to be a polished and dependable release, perfect for those who value precision and control in their creative workflow.
